charts
My charting is probably best described as a new-gen style of StepMania charting (Yolomania/NB) with far more attention paid to patterning/finger motion rather than musical relevancy (e.g. through pitch relevancy). I make a good amount of dump charts as well - with the same idea of capturing nuances in music with patterning and finger motion. Since most of these charts have more nuanced patterning, they have harder patterning than your average dump chart - a standard dump chart of mine would be something like Inferno or Bulletproof Love.

If you do want to try my charts, I'd recommend these, these tiers are representative of my enjoyment from these charts:
